snippet.textDisplay: I have a similar kind of story. Back in 2018, me and all of my coursemates are going on a field trip. But a week before the trip, i had a dream that a big fire happened and everyone was trying to save themselves but im the only one sitting there, crying helplessly cause i couldn't save my friends. And it really freaks me out. But i still go for the trip anyway. We were all in a bus in the middle of the night, in a dark road (not a highway or anything) and half way there, there's a truck caught on fire and there's a small explosion (something flew out of the truck) minutes before we pass by. And we can feel the heat from the fire while were passing by. Luckily no one got hurt,  but it is the scariest thing ever.
